casebody.data:
In the Matter of Elliott H. Pollack, a Disbarred Attorney.

[— NYS2d —]

—Application for reinstatement as an attorney and counselor-at-law in the State of New York granted only insofar as to refer this matter to the Departmental Disciplinary Committee for a hearing as indicated. No opinion. Concur—Sullivan, J. P., Milonas, Rosenberger, Ellerin and Wallach, JJ.
